        <h3 class="h--heading3">
            MAO inhibitory activity of bromo-2-phenylbenzofurans: synthesis, <em>in vitro</em> study, and docking calculations
        </h3>

        <p>
 G. L. Delogu, F. Pintus, L. May&#225;n, M. J. Matos, S. Vilar, J. Mun&#237;n, J. A. Fontenla, G. Hripcsak, F. Borges and D. Vi&#241;a,
            <i>Med. Chem. Commun.</i>, 2017,&nbsp;<strong>8</strong>, 1788

                <strong>DOI: </strong> 10.1039/C7MD00311K        </p>

<p>
